  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>There apartments are on a self catering board basis. </p>
<p>The local shops and restaurants are about 1.5 kilometres away, the nearest restaurant being around a fifteen minute walk away.</p>
<p>The hotel offers a bakery service which is booked and paid for locally.</p>
<p>Raclette and Fondue kits are available on request from the hotel reception.</p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with Huski who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a data-udi="umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575" href="/{localLink:umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575}" title="Huski - food &amp; drink delivery service">here</a> for further details.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
