  <description><![CDATA[<p>The luxurious Hameau de la Pierre Blanche Apartments in Les Houches are a great choice for families and groups looking for ski apartments with good access to the <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> ski area, they are just a short walk to the ski lifts and there is a bus stop nearby which gives you access to <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> and surrounding areas. An added bonus is there is a swimming pool and wellness facilities with a fitness area for you to make use of after skiing.</p>
<h2>Spacious and stylish</h2>
<p>These spacious and stylish apartments are located in the quiet resort of Les Houches, providing a peaceful sanctuary after a hard days skiing. Admire the view of Mont Blanc and the surrounding peaks of <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> and warm up around the fireplace in the lounge area. </p>
<p><span>The apartments are furnished to a high standard offering you comfort and convenience. All apartments have a fully equipped kitchen, lounge area and views of the surrounding area. You also have the added benefit of being able to use the wellness facilities. </span></p>
<h2>Unwind and relax</h2>
<p>A magnificent spa with a large heated swimming pool, hot tubs, sauna, and steam room is available for your enjoyment at this property. Local spa treatments and massages can also be booked locally. If relaxation is not your thing, there is also a fitness facility with an assortment of equipment.</p>]]></description>
