  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 35m². There is a twin bedroom and a pull-out sofa bed in the living area. These apartments are located on the ground floor, so will have a terrace area.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom 'Silver' Apartments</strong> sleep three to six people and are approximately 40m². There is one twin bedroom and one double bedroom and an additional pull-out sofa bed in the living area. Some apartments are duplex.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom 'Gold' Apartments</strong> sleep four to six people and are around 50m². There is one twin bedroom and one double bedroom and an additional pull-out sofa bed in the living area. These apartments have an additional shower room.</p>
<p><strong>Three Bedroom Duplex Apartments</strong> sleep four to eight people and are approximately 90m². There is one double bedroom and two twin bedrooms and an additional pull-out sofa bed in the living area. There is an additional shower and toilet room in most of these apartments.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>All occupants including babies count towards the maximum occupancy. Beds are made on arrival, except sofa beds. End of stay is included excluding the kitchen, rubbish must be taken out and beds stripped before departure. One linen set with towels is included per person, per week.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with 4-ceramic hobs, oven, fridge, dishwasher, coffee maker, kettle, kitchenware</li>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Living area</li>
<li>TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Condiment kit</li>
<li>Ski lockers</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bathrobe and slippers </li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Baby cots are available (on request) for children under 2 years old</li>
<li>Baby safety gates, bottle warmers and highchairs available on request</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
